{{!
Facebook meta tags to use when page has not facebook app to attach to.

All these meta tags have been changed to use the standard "name" attribute
instead of the non-standard "property" attribute that Facebook wants.
It should still work, but if it does not, here's why.

Guide from: http://davidwalsh.name/facebook-meta-tags
You can debug these by using: https://developers.facebook.com/tools/debug

Different page types can be found from here: 
https://developers.facebook.com/docs/opengraphprotocol/#types

}}
{{#if site.meta.facebook}}
		{{verbose "facebook meta tags, for when user links this page to fb" 2}}
{{/if}}
{{#site.meta.facebook}}
{{! Site spesific }}
		<meta name="og:type" content="{{type}}"/>
		<meta name="og:site_name" content="{{site_name}}"/>
		<meta name="og:description" content="{{description}}">
{{! Page spesific }}
		<meta name="og:url" content="{{currentURL ..}}"/>
		<meta name="og:title" content="{{../title}}"/>
{{! Site/Page image }}
		<meta name="og:image" content="{{image}}"/>
		<link rel="image_src" href="{{image}}" />{{!
If the page has an like-button, then this should come handy:
		<meta name="fb:admins" content="USER_ID1,USER_ID2"/>
If there are multiple pages, and you want them all to point to one fb-page, link this:
		<meta name="fb:app_id" content="1234567"/>

Location is useful if your pages is a business profile or about anything else with a real-world location.
		<meta name="og:latitude" content="37.416343"/>
		<meta name="og:longitude" content="-122.153013"/>
		<meta name="og:street-address" content="1601 S California Ave"/>
		<meta name="og:locality" content="Palo Alto"/>
		<meta name="og:region" content="CA"/>
		<meta name="og:postal-code" content="94304"/>
		<meta name="og:country-name" content="USA"/>

If we want to have contact details visible for facebook:
}}
{{#contact}}
	{{#email}}
		<meta name="og:email" content="{{email}}"/>
	{{/email}}
	{{#phone}}
		<meta name="og:phone_number" content="{{phone}}"/>
	{{/phone}}
	{{#fax}}
		<meta name="og:fax_number" content="{{fax}}"/>
	{{/fax}}
{{/contact}}
{{/site.meta.facebook}}